item.title: By: That girl
item.dc:creator: That girl
item.description: *rolls eyes* ok, so thier cover isn't that great. But doesn't this show that they have a whole lot of admiration for Joy Division to do a cover. A whole lot of bands look up to Joy Division and what they did. Get over it. Seriously. This doesn't make them any less musicians. And come on! A bunch of kids today wouldn't know who Joy Division is if it weren't for bands doing covers. The fan base has grown because of things like this.
